from about 8% to 14%

00:03:31.140 --> 00:03:32.820 align:middle line:90%
over the last five years.

00:03:32.820 --> 00:03:35.740 align:middle line:84%
That's not hyperinflation, but
it's what I call the slow burn.

00:03:35.740 --> 00:03:36.540 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: All right.

00:03:36.540 --> 00:03:38.820 align:middle line:84%
