00:03:47.700 --> 00:03:48.480 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Into poverty.

00:03:48.480 --> 00:03:48.810 align:middle line:90%
>>FITTS: Right.

00:03:48.810 --> 00:03:49.010 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yep, that's happening.

00:03:49.010 --> 00:03:50.610 align:middle line:90%
>>FITTS: And that's part--

00:03:50.610 --> 00:03:54.540 align:middle line:84%
the monetary inflation is part
of what has been doing that.

00:03:54.540 --> 00:03:57.960 align:middle line:84%
So that absolutely reflects
currency debasement.

00:03:57.960 --> 00:03:59.730 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: One of the
first revelations

00:03:59.730 --> 00:04:04.410 align:middle line:84%
