>>FITTS: Right.

00:47:04.770 --> 00:47:05.800 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yeah.

00:47:05.800 --> 00:47:10.410 align:middle line:84%
Are you concerned about
the future for all of us?

00:47:10.410 --> 00:47:14.040 align:middle line:84%
Let's take the $21 trillion
aside that they're hiding.

00:47:14.040 --> 00:47:17.040 align:middle line:90%
What about other things-- wars?

00:47:17.040 --> 00:47:21.090 align:middle line:84%
>>FITTS: So one of the
greatest comments I ever got--

00:47:21.090 --> 00:47:24.900 align:middle line:84%
I used to work for somebody
who was very non-critical.

00:47:24.900 --> 00:47:27.273 align:middle line:84%
