would he criticize.

00:47:27.273 --> 00:47:29.190 align:middle line:84%
But one day turned to
me, and he looked at me.

00:47:29.190 --> 00:47:30.390 align:middle line:84%
He says, you know
what your problem is?

00:47:30.390 --> 00:47:31.470 align:middle line:90%
You fret too much.

00:47:31.470 --> 00:47:33.120 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:47:33.120 --> 00:47:37.500 align:middle line:84%
So I worry about the future
in the sense that, to me--

00:47:37.500 --> 00:47:39.030 align:middle line:90%
I'm a risk manager.

00:47:39.030 --> 00:47:43.270 align:middle line:84%
