do to teach my subscribers how

00:47:43.270 --> 00:47:44.070 align:middle line:90%
to lower the risk?

00:47:44.070 --> 00:47:47.070 align:middle line:84%
Because a lot about
making money or being free

00:47:47.070 --> 00:47:48.000 align:middle line:90%
is lowering your risk.

00:47:48.000 --> 00:47:50.230 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Right, and being ready.

00:47:50.230 --> 00:47:51.030 align:middle line:90%
>>FITTS: Well--

00:47:51.030 --> 00:47:52.247 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It's so important.

00:47:52.247 --> 00:47:54.330 align:middle line:84%
>>FITTS: I don't think you
can predict the future.

00:47:54.330 --> 00:47:57.570 align:middle line:84%
I think the future is
invented, not predicted.

00:47:57.570 --> 00:48:00.122 align:middle line:84%
But the more you
can identify risks

00:48:00.122 --> 00:48:01.830 align:middle line:84%
and know how you're
going to handle them,

00:48:01.830 --> 00:48:02.738 align:middle line:90%
the more you can be--

00:48:02.738 --> 00:48:03.780 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Be ready for it.

00:48:03.780 --> 00:48:06.013 align:middle line:90%
>>FITTS: Yeah, know how to duck.

00:48:06.013 --> 00:48:07.680 align:middle line:84%
It's very important
to know how to duck.

00:48:07.680 --> 00:48:10.097 align:middle line:84%
So I'm a risk manager, because
I like to know how to duck.

00:48:10.097 --> 00:48:15.330 align:middle line:84%
But I also believe
that the future

00:48:15.330 --> 00:48:20.220 align:middle line:84%
is defined by our
spiritual power and faith.

00:48:20.220 --> 00:48:23.730 align:middle line:84%
And whatever happens,
it's going to be

00:48:23.730 --> 00:48:27.390 align:middle line:84%
what our spiritual power
and faith make happen.

00:48:27.390 --> 00:48:30.062 align:middle line:84%
So I'm much more focused
on inventing the future

00:48:30.062 --> 00:48:31.020 align:middle line:90%
than worrying about it.

00:48:31.020 --> 00:48:33.720 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You're concerned
about finances, health,

00:48:33.720 --> 00:48:35.340 align:middle line:90%
all kinds of issues, aren't you?

00:48:35.340 --> 00:48:37.470 align:middle line:84%
>>FITTS: Yeah, and one
of the reasons, George,

00:48:37.470 --> 00:48:39.210 align:middle line:90%
is for 11 years I was an--

00:48:39.210 --> 00:48:41.400 align:middle line:84%
I still do screening as
an investment advisor,

00:48:41.400 --> 00:48:45.220 align:middle line:84%
but I don't do individual
consultations anymore.

00:48:45.220 --> 00:48:47.040 align:middle line:84%
But when I did,
one of the things

00:48:47.040 --> 00:48:50.490 align:middle line:84%
I discovered is the thing
that was most harming people's

00:48:50.490 --> 00:48:54.240 align:middle line:84%
finances were
non-financial things.

00:48:54.240 --> 00:48:59.490 align:middle line:84%
So you can't look at somebody
just as a financial matter.

00:48:59.490 --> 00:49:02.100 align:middle line:84%
One of the points I
always made was-- people

00:49:02.100 --> 00:49:04.890 align:middle line:84%
would tell me that they
couldn't afford really

00:49:04.890 --> 00:49:07.240 align:middle line:90%
good, fresh food, organic food.

00:49:07.240 --> 00:49:09.180 align:middle line:90%
I was like, are you nuts?

00:49:09.180 --> 00:49:11.370 align:middle line:84%
Because while they're
having millions

00:49:11.370 --> 00:49:13.650 align:middle line:84%
sitting in their
brokerage account,

00:49:13.650 --> 00:49:16.470 align:middle line:84%
they're literally
getting physically

00:49:16.470 --> 00:49:20.850 align:middle line:84%
toxic from the
pesticides or whatever.

00:49:20.850 --> 00:49:28.830 align:middle line:84%
So I said, look, you've got
to look at your balance sheet

00:49:28.830 --> 00:49:30.660 align:middle line:90%
in a holistic way.

00:49:30.660 --> 00:49:33.180 align:middle line:84%
And you've got to look at
your children and your family.

00:49:33.180 --> 00:49:37.380 align:middle line:84%
I don't know if you know this
story, but the reason I'm alive

00:49:37.380 --> 00:49:41.070 align:middle line:84%
was when I was on Wall Street--
you know, I love making money.

00:49:41.070 --> 00:49:43.560 align:middle line:84%
Whenever anybody in my family
or friends were in trouble,

00:49:43.560 --> 00:49:45.595 align:middle line:84%
I would give them
or loan them money.

00:49:45.595 --> 00:49:46.395 align:middle line:90%
And when--

00:49:46.395 --> 00:49:47.655 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Never to get it back.

00:49:47.655 --> 00:49:49.530 align:middle line:84%
>>FITTS: Well, when the
Department of Justice

00:49:49.530 --> 00:49:55.470 align:middle line:84%
