00:50:03.060 --> 00:50:08.220 align:middle line:84%
So everybody got together and
said, well, she helped us,

00:50:08.220 --> 00:50:09.180 align:middle line:90%
so we should help her.

00:50:09.180 --> 00:50:14.070 align:middle line:84%
I had a wealthy uncle who
really financed me for 11 years.

00:50:14.070 --> 00:50:15.430 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Really, that long?

00:50:15.430 --> 00:50:15.630 align:middle line:90%
My gosh.

00:50:15.630 --> 00:50:17.588 align:middle line:84%
>>FITTS: But he said,
she helped everyone else,

00:50:17.588 --> 00:50:18.840 align:middle line:90%
so I'll help her.

00:50:18.840 --> 00:50:21.730 align:middle line:90%
I was able to pay him back.

00:50:21.730 --> 00:50:22.995 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Good for you, Cath.

00:50:22.995 --> 00:50:25.975 align:middle line:90%
>>FITTS: But I counted up--

00:50:25.975 --> 00:50:28.100 align:middle line:84%
