didn't have much money,

00:50:32.730 --> 00:50:34.840 align:middle line:84%
but they'd send me $50,
$100 a month, or whatever.

00:50:34.840 --> 00:50:35.640 align:middle line:90%
It adds up.

00:50:35.640 --> 00:50:36.723 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Just to help you.

00:50:36.723 --> 00:50:38.070 align:middle line:90%
>>FITTS: But I counted it up.

00:50:38.070 --> 00:50:40.830 align:middle line:84%
I had gifted or loaned a
quarter of a million dollars,

00:50:40.830 --> 00:50:44.067 align:middle line:84%
and that's exactly what
got gifted and paid back.

00:50:44.067 --> 00:50:45.900 align:middle line:84%
And it was that quarter
of a million dollars

00:50:45.900 --> 00:50:46.765 align:middle line:90%
that saved my life.

00:50:46.765 --> 00:50:47.640 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Interesting.

00:50:47.640 --> 00:50:50.340 align:middle line:84%
>>FITTS: So my best
investment that I ever

00:50:50.340 --> 00:50:52.715 align:middle line:84%
made was gifting and loaning
money to family and friends.

00:50:52.715 --> 00:50:53.965 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Helping other people.

00:50:53.965 --> 00:50:54.910 align:middle line:90%
>>FITTS: Yeah.

00:50:54.910 --> 00:50:58.110 align:middle line:84%
The other thing is, I'm a big
investor in people. if you

00:50:58.110 --> 00:51:01.470 align:middle line:84%
