00:51:05.550 --> 00:51:07.350 align:middle line:90%
And it's my way of saying--

00:51:07.350 --> 00:51:08.188 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Thank you.

00:51:08.188 --> 00:51:09.230 align:middle line:90%
>>FITTS: Yeah, thank you.

00:51:09.230 --> 00:51:12.420 align:middle line:84%
But also, here are good
people doing good things.

00:51:12.420 --> 00:51:15.010 align:middle line:90%
Let's help them.

00:51:15.010 --> 00:51:17.010 align:middle line:84%
