the money's on the moon.

00:51:53.350 --> 00:51:55.613 align:middle line:84%
They're liable, and
they have assets.

00:51:55.613 --> 00:51:56.655 align:middle line:90%
They have balance sheets.

00:51:56.655 --> 00:52:00.940 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: They're liable only
if somebody discloses this.

00:52:00.940 --> 00:52:03.200 align:middle line:84%
>>FITTS: Yes, but
